          <lg n="1">
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-136-083Y-line-1" n="1">Careful observers may fortel the hour,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-136-083Y-line-2" n="2">By sure prognosticks when to dread a shower:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-136-083Y-line-3" n="3">While rain depends, the pensive cat gives o'er,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-136-083Y-line-4" n="4">Her frolicks, &amp; pursues her tail no more.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-136-083Y-line-5" n="5">Returning home at night you'll find the sink,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-136-083Y-line-6" n="6">Strikes your offended nose with double stink\<hi rend="italics">cropped</hi>\</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-136-083Y-line-7" n="7">If you be wise then go not far to dine,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-136-083Y-line-8" n="8">You'll spend in Coach-hire more than saves in win\<hi rend="italics">cropped</hi>\</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-136-083Y-line-9" n="9">A coming show'r your shooting corns presage,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-136-083Y-line-10" n="10">Old akes throb, your hollow tooth will rage.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-136-083Y-line-11" n="11">om.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-136-083Y-line-12" n="12">om.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-136-083Y-line-13" n="13">Mean while the South rising with dabbling wings</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-136-083Y-line-14" n="14">A sable cloud a路thwart the welking flings.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-136-083Y-line-15" n="15">That swallowd more liquor than it coud contain</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-136-083Y-line-16" n="16">And like a drunkard gives it up again.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-136-083Y-line-17" n="17">Brisk Susan whips her linnen from the rope,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-136-083Y-line-18" n="18">While the first drizling show'r is born aslope.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-136-083Y-line-19" n="19">Such is that sprinkling which some careless quean</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-136-083Y-line-20" n="20">Flirts on you from her mop, but not so clean.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-136-083Y-line-21" n="21">You fly, invoke the gods, then turning stop,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-136-083Y-line-22" n="22">To rail; she singing, still whirls on her mop.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-136-083Y-line-23" n="23">om.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-136-083Y-line-24" n="24">om.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-136-083Y-line-25" n="25">om.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-136-083Y-line-26" n="26">om.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-136-083Y-line-27" n="27">om.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-136-083Y-line-28" n="28">om.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-136-083Y-line-29" n="29">om.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-136-083Y-line-30" n="30">om.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-136-083Y-line-31" n="31">Now in contiguous drops the flood comes down,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-136-083Y-line-32" n="32">Threat路ning with deluge this devoted Town.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-136-083Y-line-33" n="33">To shops in crouds, the dragled females fly,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-136-083Y-line-34" n="34">Pretend to cheapen goods, but nothing buy,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-136-083Y-line-35" n="35">The templer spruce while ev'ry spouts a路broach,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-136-083Y-line-36" n="36">Stays 'till 'tis fair, yet seem路s to call a coach.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-136-083Y-line-37" n="37">The tuckd up sempstress walks with hasty strides\<hi rend="italics">cropped</hi>\</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-136-083Y-line-38" n="38">While streams run down her oild umbrellas sides,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-136-083Y-line-39" n="39">Here various kinds by various fortunes led,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-136-083Y-line-40" n="40">Commence acquaintance underneath a shed.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-136-083Y-line-41" n="41">Triumphant tories, &amp; desponding whigs,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-136-083Y-line-42" n="42">Forget their fewids, &amp; join to save their wigs.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-136-083Y-line-43" n="43">Boxd in a chair the beau impatient sits,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-136-083Y-line-44" n="44">While spouts run clatt'ring o'er the roof by fits.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-136-083Y-line-45" n="45">And ever &amp; anon with frightful din.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-136-083Y-line-46" n="46">The leather sounds, he trembles from within.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-136-083Y-line-47" n="47">om.</l>
